<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ اللهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{فَتَحْرِيرُ رَقَبَةٍ مُؤْمِنَةٍ}</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>